data.description: Welcome to this charming abode, nestled into the highly desirable Churchill Elementary neighborhood of Mona Shores School District. The covered porch entry and stone fireplace greet you into the updated home, catering to your desires of both functionality and aesthetics. The heart of this property is the eat-in kitchen and dining areas, featuring granite countertops, mosaic tiled backsplash, and a stainless appliance suite, topped off with a built-in wine fridge. The upstairs bedrooms were recently redone with new trim and LVP flooring, while the partially finished basement is ready to be used as your rec room. Outside, the backyard is spacious and fenced, with a wraparound deck and shed. Set only a couple minutes from Lake Michigan beaches, this is the full package! Immediate Possession!
